
& piloting-bsuit
 
 >> Help: Piloting-BSuit (Piloting Skill)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used for piloting rolls while in a battle suit (such as swarming, charging,
 etc.).
 
 To see specifics on bsuits, type 'help bsuit'.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
